data.description: This Wrightsville home has been updated with a focus on both aesthetics and functionality. With vinyl plank flooring throughout, it not only adds a touch of luxury but is also easy to maintain.  The home has newer siding, a newer roof, and replacement windows, that enhance the home's durability and energy efficiency. Three bedrooms on the main level offer convenience, while a lower-level bedroom is perfect for someone seeking more independence. There are also additional living spaces in the lower level that can be customized to suit your family's needs. The wood deck off the kitchen allows for outdoor living during fair weather, making it convenient for outdoor meals or hosting gatherings with friends. The fenced-in backyard provides an enclosed oasis. Living in the suburbs of Wrightsville offers a peaceful and convenient lifestyle within proximity to Riverfront Park and the Susquehanna River.
